paraphrases: Can I ask how many credits is 381 ?
For EECS 381 , how many credits is it ?
How many credits do I get for 381
How many total credits do I recieve for 381 ?
If I take 381 , how many credits will I receive ?
The EECS 381 class is how many credits ?
What number of credits do I get for 381 ?
What number of credits is EECS 381 ?
What 's the number of credits for 381 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.CREDITS FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = "381" ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT COURSEalias0.CREDITS FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "department0" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = "number0" ;
